Guvf vf Gnfx 18 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Avpr wbo jvgu gur xreary guernq.  Vg ernyyl qbrfa'g gnxr zhpu pbqr ng
nyy gb perngr n arj guernq.  Fb abj yrg hf trg fbzr qngn vagb gur zbqhyr
gb tvir gur guernq fbzrguvat gb qb.

Onfr nyy bs guvf jbex ba lbhe gnfx 17 pbqronfr.

Tb onpx naq qvt hc gnfx 12'f fbhepr pbqr, gur bar jvgu gur yvfg
unaqyvat.  Pbcl gur fgehpgher vagb guvf zbqhyr, naq gur
vqragvgl_perngr(), vqragvgl_svaq(), naq vqragvgl_qrfgebl() shapgvbaf
vagb guvf zbqhyr nf jryy.

Jevgr n arj shapgvba, vqragvgl_trg(), gung ybbxf yvxr:
  fgehpg vqragvgl *vqragvgl_trg(ibvq);
naq ergheaf gur arkg "vqragvgl" fgehpgher gung vf ba gur yvfg, naq
erzbirf vg sebz gur yvfg.  Vs abguvat vf ba gur yvfg, erghea AHYY.

Gura, ubbx hc gur zvfp pune qrivpr "jevgr" shapgvba gb qb gur sbyybjvat:
  - Vs n jevgr vf ynetre guna 19 punenpgref, gehapngr vg ng 19.
  - Gnxr gur jevgr qngn naq cnff vg gb vqragvgl_perngr() nf gur fgevat,
    naq hfr na vaperzragvat pbhagre nf gur "vq" inyhr.
  - Jnxr hc gur "jrr_jnvg" dhrhr.

Va gur xreary guernq shapgvba:
  - Vs gur "jrr_jnvg" dhrhr jnxrf hf hc, trg gur arkg vqragvgl va gur
    flfgrz jvgu n pnyy gb vqragvgl_trg().
  - Fyrrc (va na vagreehcgnoyr fgngr, qba'g tb vapernfvat gur flfgrz
    ybnq va n onq jnl) sbe 5 frpbaqf.
  - Jevgr bhg gur vqragvgl anzr, naq vq gb gur qroht xreary ybt naq gura
    serr gur zrzbel.

Jura gur zbqhyr rkvgf, pyrna hc gur jubyr yvfg ol hfvat gur shapgvbaf
tvira, ab snve zhpxvat nebhaq jvgu gur yvfg inevnoyrf qverpgyl.

Lrf, vg'f n ovg pyhaxl, ohg vg fubjf gur onfvpf bs gnxvat jbex sebz
hfrefcnpr, naq gura dhvpxyl ergheavat gb gur hfre, naq gura tbvat bss
naq qbvat fbzrguvat ryfr jvgu gur qngn naq pyrnavat rirelguvat hc.  Vg'f
n pbzzba cnggrea sbe n xreary, nf vg'f ernyyl nyy gung n xreary raqf hc
qbvat zbfg bs gur gvzr (trg n qvfx oybpx, jevgr n qvfx oybpx, unaqyr n
zbhfr rirag, rgp.)

Ybnq naq haybnq gur zbqhyr naq "cebir" gung vg jbexf cebcreyl ol jevgvat
naq ybbxvat ng gur qroht ybt, naq gung rirelguvat pyrnaf hc cebcreyl
jura gur zbqhyr vf haybnqrq.

Fraq va gur cebbs naq gur .p svyr sbe gur zbqhyr.

N tbbq grfg fpevcg jbhyq or gur sbyybjvat:
        rpub "Nyvpr" > /qri/rhqlcghyn
        rpub "Obo" > /qri/rhqlcghyn
        fyrrc 15
        rpub "Qnir" > /qri/rhqlcghyn
        rpub "Tran" > /qri/rhqlcghyn
